<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://www.w3schools.com/w3css/4/w3.css">
    <title>Hobbies</title>
</head>
<body>
    {{>header}}
    
    <div class="hobby-slide-container">
        <div class="gameslide wp-caption"> 
            {{>gameslide}}
            <p class="wp-caption-text">
                Games
            </p>
        </div>
        <article class="hobby-article">
            <hr>
            <h3 class="header-align">A way to Decompress</h3>
            <p>
                During my free time I enjoy playing video games as
                a way to relieve stress and connect with long distance
                friends. I play across various platforms and enjoy a 
                variety of genres. I am by no means the best gamer, 
                however the storys are incredibly entertaining to watch 
                unfold and partake in.
            </p>
            <hr>
        </article>

        <div class="artslide wp-caption">
            {{>artslide}}
            <p class="wp-caption-text">
                Art
            </p>
        </div>
        <article class="hobby-article">
            <h3 class="header-align">Exercising Creativity</h3>
        </article>
    </div>

    {{>footer}}
</body>
</html>